documents.text:
Privacy Policy

Strictly no identifiable data is collected, or shared with a third party.


Cookies and/or local storage may be required in order to provide you with some services such as remembering user preferences. No third-party cookies are used.


This instance does not collect an access log nor an error log. Your IP address, user agent, timezone and referrer will never be logged.

Happy Searxng!
